(4, 'Sony KDL48R510C 48-Inch (47.6" Measured Diagonally) 1080p Smart LED TV (2015 Model)', 'Enjoy incredible picture quality and top notch entertainment. This elegantly slim LED TV boasts Full HD 1080p for incredible detail and Edge LED backlighting for boosted contrast. Built-in Wi-Fi lets you stream HD videos from popular services like Netflix, YouTube, and more.', '500.00'),
(5, 'TCL 32D2700 32-Inch 720p LED TV (2015 Model)', 'Enjoy The Creative Life with the TCL 32" 720p direct LED HDTV. It delivers premium picture quality and tremendous value in a sophisticated slim frame design perfect for bringing entertainment to any space. This flat screen LED HDTV features High Definition 720p resolution for a sharper image and TCL True Color Technology for brilliant color and contrast. With direct LED backlighting, view darker blacks and luminous brightness while maintaining the best standards in energy efficiency.', '200.00'),
(6, 'Vizio E24-C1 24-Inches 1080p Smart LED TV (2015 Model)', 'The all-new E-Series 24" (23.54" diag.) Edge-lit Razor LED Smart TV features an ultra-slim narrow, crystal-clear LED-lit picture, and a faster, easier-to-use Smart TV experience with built-in Wi-Fi. And not only is it smart, this TV is packed with the latest technology - like Razor LED for a brilliant picture in an ultra-thin design and Full HD 1080p for crystal-clear high definition resolution. VIZIO E-Series: Picture-Perfect, Simply Smart.', '168.00'),
(7, 'Samsung UN40J5200 40-Inch 1080p Smart LED TV (2015 Model)', 'Enjoy a viewing experience that is 2X the clarity of standard HD TVs. Enjoy a clear moving picture resolution at Motion Rate 60 with amazing refresh rate, processing speed and backlight technology. See every image as the director intended with enriched colors – even with older, non-HD content.', '399.00'),
(8, 'Samsung Galaxy Note 5 Solid Full Body Protection Case Add One PC Anti Spy Privacy Mirror Tempered Glass Screen Protector, Joylink New Design for People Who Likes Separate Case and Screen Protector', 'new design for people who likes separate case and high quality anti spy privacy mirror tempered glass screen protector, Joylink sell the durable hard case together with screen protector provide a complete protection for your Samsung galaxy note 5 cell phone', '22.98'),
(9, 'Samsung S19A10N 18.5-Inch Class CCFL Monitor - Black', 'Nah', '87.00'),
(10, 'Samsung Galaxy Grand Prime DUOS 8GB Factory Unlocked GSM Smartphone -International Version- Gray', 'The GALAXY Grand Prime has a 5 MP front camera with an ultra-wide view angle of 85 degrees. Other Features include: Wi-Fi 802.11 b/g/n, Wi-Fi Direct, Wi-Fi hotspot, Bluetooth: v4.0, A2DP, USB: micro USB v2.0, GPS: with A-GPS, Beidou, Browser: HTML5, Messaging: SMS (threaded view), MMS, Email, Push Mail, IM, Li-Ion 2600 mAh Battery, Talk time: (2G) / Up to 17 Hours (3G)', '149.67'),
(11, 'Genuine Samsung Wireless Inductive Charging Plate Pad Station (EP-PA510BWEGWW) - White', 'Say goodbye to tangled wires and lost charging cables. The Samsung Wireless Charging Pad utilizes Qi Inductive Charging Technology that eliminates the need to fumble with charging cables each time you want to charge your device.', '27.99'),
(12, 'Samsung SCH-i545 - Galaxy S4 16GB Android Smartphone - Verizon + GSM - White (Certified Refurbished)', 'This Certified Refurbished product is factory refurbished, shows limited or no wear, and includes all original accessories plus a 90-day warranty', '149.99'),
(14, 'Apple Watch Stand, Camkey Iwatch Charging Stand Aluminum Charging Dock + 2 Pack Glass Screen Protectors 42mm', 'The Camkey Apple Watch Stand features a premium build with an elegant twist. The sturdy aluminum frame provides a long-lasting place to charge and display, while the 45° viewing angle provides a convenient viewing angle whether sitting or standing. Add in hidden storage area to place your Apple Watch battery charger with specially designed cable groove to minimize cable decay, the Camkey Apple Watch Stand is the premier stand for your favorite Apple accessory.', '16.99'),
(16, 'Polobands Portable Phone Charger 6000mah Wireless Charger Power Bank Transmitter Wireless Charging Pad Power Bank with Dual USB Port for Sumsung S6 Google Nexus 5 / 4 / 7 Nokia Lumia 920-yellow', 'Quality Assurance and Satisfaction Guarantee: Certified by FCC, CE and RoHS for quality and safety, and backed by 1-year warranty. Be sure to find the official MobilePal mark to avoid counterfeits with fake battery capacity and/or inferior technology.', '45.00'),
