(26, 'LP Wireless Bluetooth 4.0 Hands-Free Car Kit Car Speakphones with Aux Input Jack (3.5 mm)-Support 2 phone connection', 'LP Wireless Bluetooth4.0 Hands-Free Car Kit is one car speakphone with Aux Input Jack (3.5 mm). It is designed to provide a simple hands-free solution to answering and receiving phone calls in your car. It also streams stereo music from your smartphone, tablet or other Bluetooth capable devices to your car audio system. Key Features - Hands-free car kit, designed for cars - Bluetooth4.0, capable to connect any bluetooth smartphones/tablets. - High qulity sound: Built-in noisy-cancellation circuit - Answer/receive incoming calls - Stream music from any Bluetooth capable device - Music player controls - Play, Pause, Previous song, Next song. - Recharge your device while listening to music via USB port Note: The car kit requires a 3.5 mm input jack in the car stereo Compatibility: - All iPhones, iPads and iPod Touch - Android smartphones - HTC, All Droids, Samsung - Blackberry smartphones - All Bluetooth capable devices(br/) Package including: - LP Bluetooth Car Kit - Adhesive pad (for mounting) - Dual-port car charger (1x2.1A USB port, 1x 1A USB port) <>br- 2 in 1 cable (USB cable+3.5mm jack cable) - User manual', '18.49'),
(27, 'Samsung Gear S2 Smartwatch for Most Android Phones - Dark Gray', 'With elegant curves and premium finishes, the Samsung Gear S2 will turn heads. The circular interface and rotating bezel give you effortless navigation, so you can quickly access the things that are most important to you. This intuitive interface lets you easily access important notifications, texts, and updates from your phone with just a glance at your wrist. The built-in S-Health app tracks your steps, your heart rate, and even gives you a nudge when it’s time to get moving. And with built-in wireless charging, it’s easy to keep the Gear S2 powered up. Whether you’re at home, work or anywhere in between, you can power up by simply setting your Gear S2 on the included wireless charging dock. Plus, with easily customizable watch faces, you can customize the Gear S2 to fit your unique style. With powerful capabilities and sleek looks, the Gear S2 will help you get the most out of your day.', '279.99'),
(28, 'Kindle Paperwhite, 6" High-Resolution Display (300 ppi) with Built-in Light, Wi-Fi - Includes Special Offers', '', '119.99'),
