(207, 'Acer Aspire Switch 10 SW5-012 10.1" Laptop 2GB 64GB | SW5-012-13TT (Certified Refurbished)', 'The Acer Aspire Switch 10 is a 2-in-1 tablet device that offers your mobility, portability and productivity in a lightweight and elegant package. With the magnetically detachable keyboard, this versatile tablet can be positioned and switched between four distinct modes - tablet, notebook, tent and display modes - to suit your specific needs. The quad-core Intel Atom processor gets your everyday tasks done quickly, and the 10.1" IPS touch screen brings everything you see to life with 1280 x 800 resolution and bold, accurate color. The screen also features Gorilla Glass 3 casing for protection against scratches, and Acer LumiFlex technology for clear, brilliant display even outside under the sun. Plus, with low weight, thin profile and brushed aluminum design, the Switch 10 is the perfect digital companion for your on-the-go lifestyle.', '211.99'),
(208, '2016 Newest Acer 2-in-1 11.6-inch High Performance Touchscreen convertible Laptop or Tablet, Intel Quad-Core Pentium Processor, 4GB DDR3, 500GB HDD, Bluetooth, HDMI, Windows 10, 8 hrs Battery Life', 'Flip for it: With its 360-degree dual-torque hinge, the Acer Aspire R 11 flips the view full circle for multiple ways to use it. Its versatility makes it the perfect device for collaborating and sharing, and with Windows 10, you get easy ways to snap apps in place, create new desktops, and work and play across all your devices. Four ways to use it Work in Notebook mode, share in Display mode, prop it up for a movie in Tent mode, or use it like a tablet in Pad mode. Ultraportable sidekick Just 0.8 inches thin and only 3 pounds, the R 11 fits perfectly in your bag, and has a full-size keyboard for working in comfort. Color: Sky Blue Processor & Memory: Intel Pentium N3700 1.60 GHz with Intel Burst Technology up to 2.40 GHz 4GB DDR3L 1600 MHz Operating System: Windows 10 Home, 64-bit Drives: 500GB 5400 RPM HDD No Optical Drive Graphics & Video: 11.6 in LED touchscreen (1366 x 768), 10-finger multi-touch support Intel HD Graphics with shared graphics memory Communications: 802.11ac (Miracast enabled) + Bluetooth 4.0 1MP 720p webcam Audio: Integrated Audio Processing Ports & Slots: 1x USB 3.0 1x USB 2.0 1x HDMI-Out 1x SD card reader 1x Headphone output/Microphone input combo Battery: 4-cell lithium-prismatic (up to 8 hours) Additional Information: Dimensions: 11.70 x 8.30 x 0.82 in (297.18 x 210.82 x 20.82 mm) Approximate Weight: 3.31 lbs (1.50 kg)', '319.00'),
(209, 'Acer Aspire 15.6-Inch Gaming Laptop (Intel Core i5-5200U, 8GB, 1TB HDD, Windows 10), Black / Grey', 'Designed to Accelerate With premium performance and stunning visuals, the new 5th gen Intel Core i5 processors has the power to take your computing to a new level. Equipped with the latest 802.11ac wireless technology, experience up to 3x faster performance, when connected to an 802.11ac based router, making everything from online gaming to streaming video both faster and more reliable. Affordable all around gaming laptop. NVIDIA GeForce 940M graphics with 2GB of discrete video memory gives games an adrenaline shot with incredible performance and futuristic, visually-stunning graphics. Experience heart-pounding, cinematic visuals on your favorite games. Tech specs Display: 15.6 in LED-backlit with CineCrystalTM 1920 x 1080 Processor:Intel Core i5-5200U 2.20 GHz with Turbo Boost Technology up to 2.70 GHz Memory:8GB DDR3L SDRAM Hard drive size:1TB 5400 RPM HDD Video:NVIDIA GeForce 940M (Dedicated 2 GB video memory) Operating system:Windows 10 Home, 64-bit Optical drive: None Media drive:Digital Media Card Reader - Secure DigitalTM (SD) Card Audio:Acer TrueHarmony High-Performance Sound System Ports:2 USB 3.0, 1 USB 2.0, HDM. Headphone output/Microphone input combo LAN Gigabit Ethernet (10/100/1000) Battery:4-cell lithium-ion (5 hour runtime) Camera:720p webcam Wireless:802.11ac/a/b/g/n Bluetooth:Bluetooth 4.0 Dimensions:15.02 x 10.08 x 1.15 in Weight:5.29 lbs Color:Black (exterior) / Grey (interior)', '569.92');
