(233, 'Colgate Wisp Portable Mini-Brush Max Fresh, Peppermint, 24 Count', 'Colgate wisp is your go-to brush for on-the-go. Its built-in peppermint bead releases minty freshness while its bristles gently remove food and other particles. No water or rinsing necessary making it perfect for while you are out and about.', '4.96'),
