(235, 'Colgate 360 Degree Adult Full Head Toothbrush, Soft, 4 Count', 'Colgate 360 Full Head Toothbrush, Soft, 4 Pack. Unique cheek and tongue cleaner helps remove over 96% more bacteria (vs. brushing teeth alone with a flat-trim toothbrush). Tightly packed, tapered bristles and polishing cups help remove more plaque and stains than an ordinary toothbrush. Cleans teeth, cheeks, tongue and gums.', '7.53'),
