(237, 'Colgate Extra Clean Toothbrush, Full Head, Medium, 6 Count', 'The Colgate Extra Clean Toothbrush offers great cleaning at an affordable price. This brush features a cleaning tip, specially designed to clean hard-to-reach areas and polished, end-rounded bristles designed to effectively clean while protecting enamel and gums.', '5.99'),
